text.tspan: One morning, as Gregor Samsa was waking up from anxious
dreams, he discovered that in bed he had been changed into a
monstrous verminous bug. He lay on his armour-hard back and
saw, as he lifted his head up a little, his brown, arched abdomen
divided up into rigid bow-like sections.
